## ğŸš€ Setup Instructions

### 1ï¸âƒ£ Log into VM & Install Dependencies

```bash
sudo yum install docker -y
sudo yum install git -y
```

### 2ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone <this-git-repo-link>
cd <repo-name>
```

### 3ï¸âƒ£ Configure Docker on VM

```bash
sudo service docker start
sudo usermod -aG docker $USER
```

> âš ï¸ After adding the user to the `docker` group, **log out and log back in** for changes to take effect.

### 4ï¸âƒ£ Build Docker Image

```bash
docker build -t visitor-app .
```

### 5ï¸âƒ£ Create a Docker Network

```bash
